{"tid":906463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（我的英雄學院小心）等我黎教點樣駁返火影狗反自己套動漫","createTime":"2018-11-18T04:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T11:44:37.000Z","uid":9601,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d0d9f5bc2561e0078b7d7a099fa4e01c50ef4d","tid":906463,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1GhRH5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1GhRH5.png&h=8fc3042d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢地遲下可能會反 主角5%唔夠打就用100%  當100%唔夠打就開一百萬% 跟住收皮<br />\n但大家可以用以下句野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YnkOdXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnkOdXC.png&h=ff8ff9b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實螺旋丸係鳴門絕招黎 用呢招做根底發展有咩咁出奇？<br />\n你睇咩漫畫都係咁<br />\n照你咁講 咩漫畫既主角都係on9 <br />\n浪客劍心飛天御劍流 龍珠 龜波氣功 hxh小岡 猜猜拳 我的英雄學院 one for all <br />\n冇左螺旋丸個個仲係鳴門？<br />\n小岡唔出猜猜拳唔通出星爆氣流斬咩<br />\n要反火影都唔好用呢d藉口啦<br />\n用下個腦再諗過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改一改啲主角名就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ff8593674a1a072c6af3ba5e9bd3e9a32668b2","tid":906463,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd748b78b778072d1d4a13ecd3277e52f51b3f61","tid":906463,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"一拳連招都無, 衝埋去齋揼, 垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2194658ca61df2386d59596c79edc042cddb10c","tid":906463,"uid":127075,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔好再開post好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係叫你用下個腦"},{"pid":"bec877589b368f0d7c5022e4858f7edfe0723378","tid":906463,"uid":9601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd748b78b778072d1d4a13ecd3277e52f51b3f61","tid":906463,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score